Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Located on the doorstep of Sydney’s famous Circular Quay in The Rocks, 66 Harrington Street enjoys the relaxed village-style atmosphere of The Rocks, with the strategic convenience to the CBD Financial Core.

66 Harrington Street presents a unique leasing opportunity for the savvy corporate occupier.

A 5,973sqm whole building leasing opportunity – a statement for your new company HQ. Flexible part building leasing opportunities are also available.

Complemented by a major building upgrade in 2017, 66 Harrington Street offers five levels of modern ABW-style fitout with contemporary End-of Trip facilities, storage and exclusive use rooftop terrace overlooking Circular Quay.

Rich in history and character, The Rocks precinct provides an array of fine restaurants, cafes and retail stores with excellent access to Circular Quay ferry wharfs, train station and light rail.

Please call exclusive leasing agents CBRE for more information.
